            underlying canvas. Elements that occupy a ruled manuscript line are tagged with the 
            attribute <code>@corresp="#canvasline"</code>, where <code>#canvasline</code> references a category in a 
            taxonomy of "graphic features" in the <gi>teiHeader</gi></p>
